---
layout: default
title: Blog
subline: Everything you need to know about the agility of the IT domain.
---

<section class="text-gray-700 bg-gradient-to-t from-gray-800  to-gray-900">
  <div class="container mx-auto lg:py-16 py-8 px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:mb-12 w-full text-center max-w-screen-lg mx-auto">
      <h1
        class="page-headline"
      >
      {{title}}
      </h1>
      <p class="mx-auto md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-gray-400 lg:w-2/3">
        {{subline}}
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="container px-5 md:py-24 mx-auto">
  <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-2 grid-cols-1">
    {% set postslist = collections.post %} {% for post in postslist | reverse %}
      <div
        class="h-full shadow-xl bg-gray-800 border-opacity-60 rounded-lg overflow-hidden"
      >
        <img
          class="lg:h-48 md:h-36 w-full object-cover object-center"
          src="{{ post.data.thumbnail }}"
          alt="blog"
        />
        <div class="p-6">
          {% for tag in post.data.tags %} {%- if tag != "post" -%} {% set tagUrl
          %}/tags/{{ tag }}/{% endset %}
          <h2
            class="inline uppercase tracking-wide text-xs title-font font-medium text-gray-400 mb-1"
          >
            {{ tag }}
          </h2>
          {%- endif -%} {% endfor %}
          <h1 class="title-font text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-100 mb-3">
            {% if post.data.title %} {{ post.data.title }} {% else %} Untitled
            {% endif %}
          </h1>
          <p class="leading-relaxed mb-3 text-gray-400">
            <time class="inline font-bold">
              {{ post.date | readableDate }} by <a>{{ post.data.author }}</a>
            </time>
            - Photo booth fam kinfolk cold-pressed sriracha leggings jianbing
            microdosing tousled waistcoat.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center flex-wrap">
            <a href="{{post.url}}" class="text-primary-400 inline-flex font-bold items-center md:mb-2 lg:mb-0 hover:underline"
              >Read article
              <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 ml-2"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                fill="none"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
              >
                <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
                <path d="M12 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div>